title: Templaza TZ Young Fitness Template (Joomla 3.x)
description:
Fitness Template is the responsive Joomla template that is used for the needs of the development of websites on health problems, gymnasium, spa and other purposes. This is the best opportunity to introduce your website to everyone if you use our product.

Responsive Design
All pages are designed and developed to the Bootstrap Framework to display perfectly across all devices and screen sizes. If preferred this can be display easily in template manager.

Phoca Gallery
Phoca Gallery is a Joomla! gallery - image gallery for Joomla! CMS. It includes component, modules and plugins and allows users to display images or Youtube videos in many different styles.

Multi Slideshow
You can display images according to the slide or fade effect with two different styles for Fitness template or Spa template.

2 Home Page Options
Having two homepage styles in accordance with users' different purposes.

6 Colour Styles
You will have a chance to create website with your favorite color because Young Fitness has 6 colour styles. Wow! It is wonderful option, Discover it
